'''''Aeglos''''', or '''''aiglos''''', means "Snowthorn" or "icicle" in [[Sindarin]] (from ''[[aeg]]'', "point" and ''[[loss]]'', "snow") and may refer to:

==Middle-earth==
* [[Aeglos (plant)|Aeglos]], a plant common to [[West Beleriand]].
* '''[[Aeglos (spear)|Aeglos]], the spear of [[Gil-galad|Ereinion Gil-galad]].'''
==Fandom==
* ''[[Aiglos (journal)]]'', the annual journal of the ''Parmadili'', the [[Sekcja Tolkienowska ŚKF|Tolkien Section of the Silesian Fantasy Club]].
